    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189450/extras/製作各式手搖飲!_8.png?t=1764685940\" /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189450/extras/012891e988bc210e4f391dbdfda85004.avif?t=1764685940\" width=615 height=105 /></span>在《奶茶店模拟器》中，你可以：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     ● 制作各种类型的饮料，添加不同的配料，并尽量让顾客满意。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     ● 妥善管理时间，添加适量的配料。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     ● 饮料的质量会影响你的得分和店铺的受欢迎程度。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     ● 游戏内的音效和搞笑的物理效果让制作饮料变得有趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189450/extras/b6c2e6ae5217b9a617b11c5b6b305893.poster.avif?t=1764685940\" width=800 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189450/extras/b6c2e6ae5217b9a617b11c5b6b305893.webm?t=1764685940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189450/extras/b6c2e6ae5217b9a617b11c5b6b305893.mp4?t=1764685940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189450/extras/7cb1d5ce2a395783bbd379fb561c31eb.avif?t=1764685940\" width=615 height=105 /></span>成为店主并不容易，你需要：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     ● 补充各种类型的物资和消耗品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     ● 煮茶并清理你制造的混乱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     ● 找到自己的节奏来完成杂务，这是成功奶茶店的关键。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189450/extras/ea95cc642f5a044eaf6b2d638745ad7c.poster.avif?t=1764685940\" width=800 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189450/extras/ea95cc642f5a044eaf6b2d638745ad7c.webm?t=1764685940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189450/extras/ea95cc642f5a044eaf6b2d638745ad7c.mp4?t=1764685940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189450/extras/d6d27f71d11b0034b788017f0fad7508.avif?t=1764685940\" width=615 height=105 /></span>在装饰和家具上花钱是个好主意，顾客喜欢干净和时尚的店铺。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     ● 你可以将物品放置在任何地方，打造你独一无二的奶茶店。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189450/extras/ee97f3d939c702f814bfefba910e3f3f.poster.avif?t=1764685940\" width=800 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189450/extras/ee97f3d939c702f814bfefba910e3f3f.webm?t=1764685940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189450/extras/ee97f3d939c702f814bfefba910e3f3f.mp4?t=1764685940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189450/extras/eeb4f3ffba092778d565db8b0085abd9.avif?t=1764685940\" width=615 height=105 /></span>通过完成不同的任务，你可以解锁更多种类的茶和任务，完成任务也可以增加你店铺的受欢迎程度。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     ● 在任务期间做出明智的选择，也会影响你店铺未来的表现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189450/extras/3dc0d05463f25d8d25aaa1bd70e78df6.poster.avif?t=1764685940\" width=800 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189450/extras/3dc0d05463f25d8d25aaa1bd70e78df6.webm?t=1764685940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189450/extras/3dc0d05463f25d8d25aaa1bd70e78df6.mp4?t=1764685940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
